 |apocalypse 3 · 15.o9.-16.o9.o1 · "na radosti" pub · brandys n/labem · CZ|
 `------------------------------------------------------------------------'

 Welcome back!!

After a one year break we're back and rocking with the next pure Amiga 
old-skool scene party named "Apocalypse". There was not many visitors last
year due to a very badly chosen date (we held our party just a week after




















the famous Mekka-Symposium in Germany), so now we've decided to move
Apocalypse back to September, which seemed to be the best.

The party will be held in the same place as last time, so I hope everybody
will be able to get there without our help ;). Ask us, if you have trouble
finding the place.

What will take place at Apocalypse 3?

Compos, music show with three (or more) DJs(including the czech
"Luxor System"). The czech PC DJ "X-Brain" (or Mozex) promised to come.
We can also promise a big screen and a nice sound at the partyplace, which
has a nice garden as always. We hope to organize some music improvization as
last time, using instruments brought by the visitors. If you have some ideas
how to make some more fun, then contact us. We can make a contract ;).

Check compos, limits and rules below.

All important information:
--------------------------





















Date: 15.-16.9.2oo1
Partyplace: "Na radosti" pub
Street: Kralovicka 485
Town: Brandys nad Labem (20 mins by car or bus from Prague)
Country: The Czech Republic
Price: 120 CZK (or 6DM)

Things to bring along:  Harddisks and floppies containing the 
                        compo-entries, sleeping bags, money  ;), computers
                        (please reserve a seat using our e-mails or 
                        telephones as soon as possible!)

Strictly prohibited:    Private alcohol supply at the partyplace (the
                        partyplace prices are reasonably low), drug abuse at
                        the partyplace, smoking ANYthing in the hall.

Start itching for:      Compos, live music, the cheapest beer ever as always
                        ;), cheap food, foreign sceners from Poland, Germany
                        and Spain (maybe), big screen, good sound.




















Any damages you inflict will have to be paid at the very place!

